{"tid":2421263,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"牛腱係咪攤凍哂先好切？","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T13:45:48.000Z","uid":373442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"08f7d7f3d496489494382ea617d8a0d74c8b2a87","tid":2421263,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"今日滷牛腱<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時整滷水我習慣煮完再由佢浸幾個鐘<br />\n<br />\n之前試過趕時間牛腱仲熱就切，切得好衰，當時我認為因為辣手同把刀唔夠利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日切果陣舊牛腱微暖，琴日磨左刀，好過上次，但都係整唔到係街食果啲咁薄咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但切落好明顯手感唔同，係咪攤凍哂或者雪一晚再切會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rtjxLr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rtjxLr.jpg&h=2cec1146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49f392c0190637440e4b61f3b5a038ee0114ce09","tid":2421263,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"要用水之呼吸"},{"pid":"de1313e560fc0c91684821ffc9b1ddefa06ccbac","tid":2421263,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"肥牛都要雪到冰先切得薄，何況你哩舊咁厚嘅嘢"},{"pid":"ad2298705ed6043f2e7c8453c4d77b57d00a626e","tid":2421263,"uid":168939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f7d7f3d496489494382ea617d8a0d74c8b2a87","tid":2421263,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"今日滷牛腱<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時整滷水我習慣煮完再由佢浸幾個鐘<br />\n<br />\n之前試過趕時間牛腱仲熱就切，切得好衰，當時我認為因為辣手同把刀唔夠利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日切果